{"id": "1421604439554527232", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "personally I don't think capital-C Card is a deliberate choice", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T21:08:30.523000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421604547830223098", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think it's more a byproduct of translation key phrases (like Command Card is probably just a named term so it just gets capitalized when translated)", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T21:08:56.338000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421604619783770193", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think it'd be fine to drop the capitalization honestly", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T21:09:13.493000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421604734263103601", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'd much rather lose the capitalization than see something say \"Destroy a Card\" because that just looks *wonky*", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T21:09:40.787000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "BennettThumbsUp", "emoji_id": "773345984474120202", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421579151529480212", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I feel like we need different words for when an Awakener has been Roused (as in, their Rouse card is in the deck) and when an Awakener has been Roused (as in, you have played their Rouse card). In Astral Reign we at least have \"Gnosis Rouse\"... As much as I like \"For each Awakener that has been Roused\" for flavor, I feel like it needs to be more clear.\n\n> At the start of battle, for each <:warn:1408311425952387122>Rouse Card in the deck, <:realmmastery:1408309232935374879>Realm Mastery increases by 35. When you play an Awakener's <:warn:1408311425952387122>Rouse Card, conjure 2 of their Command Cards at random; they have <:warn:1408311425952387122>Exhaust.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:28:01.388000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421579151004930181", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 114510, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1421579151004930181/image.png?ex=6a324c81&is=6a30fb01&hm=e5bd69695d09746b5f512a8061d6602bcfd90ed33cae77bd2754058fc3da9627&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421585461096480778", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "agreed, but the \"conjure\" keyword really does not fit Morimens flavorwise...", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:53:05.706000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["183782216353054720"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421579151529480212", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421585502976606359", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "feels a bit too MtG-knockoff-y to me", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:53:15.691000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421585576259358760", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "maybe for Casiah but there isn't much magic otherwise", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:53:33.163000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421585636263067759", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "I feel like \"create\" and \"obtain\" are perfectly fine neutral keywords", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:53:47.469000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421586089680044133", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "maybe \"generate\" but that also doesn't really fit that well", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:55:35.572000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421586601758167132", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "if you really wanted to use fancy terms for flavor, \"breed\" or \"originate\" would probably fit Morimens aesthetic better while not really being any more readable than conjure but honestly i can't see any reason not to use create", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:57:37.661000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-27T19:58:27.223000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421597270473707521", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "hard disagree on \"breed\" and \"originate\", like... what? \nI was going to use Create for effects that make a non-temporary copy of a card (Gland Division, Mirror), and Conjure for those that make temporary copies. \nMy honest rebuttal is that \"Obtain\", \"Add\" and \"Shuffle\" reek of MTL. \"Generate\" will be used to relatively reference when effects produce something (\"STR generation\", \"Aliemus generated by Awakeners' effects\", etc)\nOf course \"Shuffle\" would need to be used *in conjunction* with another keyword (create and shuffle a copy into the draw pile) but it shouldn't be used on its own.\nIf you don't like it I'm fine with skipping Conjure and having every instance of this effect always use Create, since we'd have to specify Exhaust or Fleeting for those effects anyway, I just liked the flavor.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T20:40:01.281000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421597897715355748", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "> hard disagree on \"breed\" and \"originate\", like... what? \nthey are hugely significant lore terms and have significantly more relevance to Morimens worldbuilding than conjure, since Morimens doesn't really have any magical elements to it", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T20:42:30.827000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421598005638856835", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "do not the cards", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T20:42:56.558000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
